snippet.title: Judge sides with Johnny Depp: ACLU must reveal if Amber Heard donated $7M divorce settlement
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp has notched a victory in his lengthy legal battle against ex-wife Amber Heard. 
A New York judge has partially granted a petition from the "Pirates of the Caribbean" star to determine if Heard donated the entirety of her $7 million divorce settlement to the American Civil Liberties Unio
